\caption{%
  \textbf{ROC and Precision-Recall curves for four binary classifiers.}
  Left: receiver operating characteristic (ROC) curves; dotted diagonal marks random performance.
  Right: precision-recall (PRC) curves; dotted horizontal line marks the random baseline (prevalence $= 0.40$).
  AUROC and average precision (AP) are reported in each legend entry.
  \textbf{OursModel achieves the highest AUROC and AP across all four methods.}
  Each method's scores were computed from $n_+ = 120$ positive and $n_- = 180$ negative examples
  drawn from \texttt{data.json}; curves are computed without cross-validation (single split).
}

